Michelle,

 We had the pretrial hearing today before Judge Kaufman.  He granted
our Motion to continue the trial date.
The new date is February 20, 2001.  The next pretrial conference is
scheduled February 2, 2000, and all of the depositions must be completed by
that date.  I further informed the Judge that Enron would make George
